Package jinngine.geometry.contact

Interface Summary
ContactGenerator A contact generator is used by the ContactConstraint to generate its contact information.
ContactGeneratorClassifier A ContactGeneratorClassifier is used by the model to map between pairs of interfering geometries, and suited ContactGenerator instances, used by the ContactConstraint.
 

Class Summary
BulletNativeContactGenerator  
ContactGenerator.ContactPoint A simple structure class representing a contact point with a normal and a penetration depth
SphereContactGenerator Simple, fast, sphere-sphere contact generator.
SupportMapContactGenerator  
SupportMapSphereContactGenerator Contact generator for Sphere-SupportMap combinations.
